{"data": [{"id": "4743742", "title": "CGDV: Light On Dividends But An Excellent Mix Of Growth And Value", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Focus on fundamentals\" data-id=\"826530516\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tang90246</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4678621-cgdv-top-performing-dividend-etf-with-excellent-earnings-growth-potential\">last reviewed</a> the Capital Group Dividend Value ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CGDV\" title=\"Capital Group Dividend Value ETF\">CGDV</a></span>) on March 15, 2024, when I reiterated my \"buy\" rating due to its solid combination of growth and value. Since my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4636449-cgdv-actively-managed-dividend-etf-beating-the-market\">initial coverage</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/826530516/image_826530516.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743742-cgdv-light-on-dividends-but-an-excellent-mix-of-growth-and-value", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:52:00"}, {"id": "4743744", "title": "Crocs' Valuation Can Be Capitalized On In The Near Term", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sand &amp; sandals\" data-id=\"173831350\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">cunfek/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Crocs (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CROX\" title=\"Crocs, Inc.\">CROX</a></span>) is a unique footwear company with a distinct brand and potential for international growth. However, given slower growth rates after a large increase in brand awareness from the pandemic, the company isn't a growth investment</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173831350/image_173831350.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743744-crocs-stock-valuation-can-be-capitalized-on-in-near-term", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:48:02"}, {"id": "4743741", "title": "Tracking Baker Brothers Portfolio - Q3 2024 Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pharmaceuticals Medical Stock Market Industry Sector Wall Street Buildings 3d Illustration\" data-id=\"1160060870\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5000px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">iQoncept</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This article is part of a series that provides an ongoing analysis of the changes made to Baker Brothers\u2019 13F stock portfolio on a quarterly basis. It is based on Baker Brothers\u2019 regulatory <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1263508/000110465924118899/0001104659-24-118899-index.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">13F Form</a> filed on 11/14/2024. The</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1160060870/image_1160060870.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743741-tracking-baker-brothers-portfolio-q3-2024-update", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:38:23"}, {"id": "4743750", "title": "CPI Bullish For Long-Term Inflation Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with the words CPI on coins stack. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth with relate icon.\" data-id=\"1733234018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Boy Wirat</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>CPI printed in-line at .3 on core and headline. Importantly, rent and owners' equivalent rent finally declined to .2 for the month. Other volatile components such as new and used cars, lodging and airline fares were elevated.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743750-cpi-bullish-for-long-term-inflation-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:20:00"}, {"id": "4743738", "title": "Sun Hung Kai Properties: A Solid Bet On Recovery In Hong Kong And China", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone view of Hong Kong city\" data-id=\"1267068394\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">CHUNYIP WONG/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/tudor-invest-holdings/analysis?ticker=SUHJY\">We have covered</a> Sun Hung Kai Properties (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SUHJY\" title=\"Sun Hung Kai Properties Limited\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:SUHJY</a>) since 2022, and maintained a bullish view about the stock, despite the tumultuous times that Hong Kong has been going through.</p> <p>Tourism to the city</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1267068394/image_1267068394.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743738-sun-hung-kai-properties-stock-solid-bet-recovery-hong-kong-china", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 07:07:15"}, {"id": "4743737", "title": "Amazon: Why I Am Aggressively Accumulating At All-Time Highs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Amazon fulfillment center building in Las Vegas\" data-id=\"1252468735\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8256px\" height=\"5504px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">4kodiak/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Amazon (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a></span>)(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NEOE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN:CA\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN:CA</a></span>) has reached a new all-time high lately on strong optimism about the U.S. economy following the win of President Trump as well as broadly falling inflation. Amazon, as a major e-Commerce platform, is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252468735/image_1252468735.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743737-amazon-stock-why-am-aggressively-accumulating-at-all-time-highs", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 06:56:38"}, {"id": "4743743", "title": "CPI: Shelter Prices Are Rising 4.7% YoY", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with CPI word and stack of coins and increasing graph with shopping cart icon. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth\" data-id=\"2078053280\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ratana21</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This analysis takes the BLS inflation data and recalculates the percentage changes at the category level to get unrounded numbers. The total number ties to the BLS, but it gives more detail at the granular level.</p> <h2>November CPI</h2>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078053280/image_2078053280.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743743-cpi-shelter-prices-are-rising-4-7-percent-yoy", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 06:55:00"}, {"id": "4743736", "title": "IYR: Overlooked Real Estate Fundamentals And Technical Tailwinds Heading Into 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view over houses in Paris suburb\" data-id=\"1500297506\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gary Yeowell</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Shares of companies from the Real Estate sector have struggled compared to the stout returns of the S&amp;P 500 in the last five years. COVID obviously dealt a massive blow to the broad property index, and subsequent weakness in</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1500297506/image_1500297506.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743736-iyr-etf-overlooked-real-estate-fundamentals-technical-tailwinds-heading-into-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 06:33:16"}, {"id": "4743739", "title": "November CPI Report: Inflation Risks Keep The Fed On Edge", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"CPI, consumer price index concept. Wooden block with the words CPI on coins stack. Goods price inflation and inflation rising. Impact on economic growth with relate icon.\" data-id=\"1733234018\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1733234018/image_1733234018.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_i